      "comment": "MIDNIGHT GHOST (7) is a promising dog in the frame at one of nine starts including five wins and was in the minors again latest (20.53) over 365m at this track. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. EDDY SPAGHETTI (6) was below best last time finishing fourth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Can improve sharply here. ZIPPING GEORGIA (3) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 365m at this track beaten 5.5 lengths (21.24) behind Glorified in a Grade 5 on June 18. Racing well and deserves a win. FIREFLY GAL (1) will be hard to beat with a drop in trip.",
